WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.840 --> 00:00:08.257
<i>Earth.</i>

2
00:00:08.258 --> 00:00:11.510
<i>A cradle
for unimaginable beauty</i>

3
00:00:11.511 --> 00:00:14.763
<i>and staggering wonder.</i>

4
00:00:14.764 --> 00:00:18.475
<i>Incomprehensible.
overwhelming.</i>

5
00:00:18.476 --> 00:00:23.731
<i>this planet mocks our
feeble power to describe it.</i>

6
00:00:23.732 --> 00:00:28.945
<i>Yes. to truly appreciate
the astounding grandeur</i>

7
00:00:28.946 --> 00:00:34.159
<i>of this planet.
sometimes you must defile it.</i>

8
00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:37.536
<i>Behold the defiler.</i>

9
00:00:37.537 --> 00:00:43.460
<i>His character is vile.
base. and depraved.</i>

10
00:00:43.461 --> 00:00:45.836
<i>Once a proud talk show host.</i>

11
00:00:45.837 --> 00:00:49.340
<i>he has been driven
by a changing ecosystem</i>

12
00:00:49.341 --> 00:00:52.844
<i>to a drier
and harsher climate...</i>

13
00:00:52.845 --> 00:00:55.637
<i>the weekly podcast.</i>

14
00:00:55.638 --> 00:01:01.144
<i>Here. without the nourishment
of his studio audience.</i>

15
00:01:01.145 --> 00:01:05.439
<i>this clown
with dull. tiny eyes.</i>

16
00:01:05.440 --> 00:01:08.317
<i>the eyes
of a crudely painted doll.</i>

17
00:01:08.318 --> 00:01:12.614
<i>is forced to feed
on that meagerest of morsels.</i>

18
00:01:12.615 --> 00:01:15.699
<i>the random call-in fan.</i>

19
00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.830
<i>Unhinged by the feral scent
of their mild enthusiasm.</i>

20
00:01:20.831 --> 00:01:25.542
<i>he scavenges
in distant lands uninvited.</i>

21
00:01:25.543 --> 00:01:29.297
<i>fueled by a bottomless hunger
for recognition</i>

22
00:01:29.298 --> 00:01:32.029
<i>and the occasional selfie.</i>

23
00:01:32.030 --> 00:01:35.856
<i>[dramatic music]</i>

24
00:01:35.857 --> 00:01:39.682
<i>♪ ♪</i>

25
00:01:39.683 --> 00:01:42.476
<i>This is madness.</i>

26
00:01:42.477 --> 00:01:44.687
<i>This is lunacy.</i>

27
00:01:44.688 --> 00:01:46.606
<i>This is chaos.</i>

28
00:01:50.235 --> 00:01:53.780
<i>This is
"Conan O'Brien Must Go."</i>

29
00:01:56.408 --> 00:01:58.575
<i>Thailand.</i>

30
00:01:58.576 --> 00:01:59.576
